        "raw_5469fe65fe36d61a"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "prior": 0.9
      },
      "package": "galileo_fine",
      "parameters": [],
      "representative_content": "日常生活中，石头比羽毛下落更快，铁球比木球更快。",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "obs.daily",
          "module": "default",
          "package": "galileo_fine",
          "version": "4.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "observation",
      "knowledge_type": "claim",
      "local_canonical_id": "lcn_e713a8d8ca496f0b",
      "member_raw_node_ids": [
        "raw_e384821b08ebd7f4"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "prior": 0.9
      },
      "package": "galileo_fine",
      "parameters": [],
      "representative_content": "在不同介质中比较轻重物体的下落，介质越稠密速度差异越明显；越稀薄差异越不明显。",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "obs.media",
          "module": "default",
          "package": "galileo_fine",
          "version": "4.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "observation",
      "knowledge_type": "claim",
      "local_canonical_id": "lcn_f3db8ee23301df87",
      "member_raw_node_ids": [
        "raw_10d06d805e009860"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "prior": 0.9
      },
      "package": "galileo_fine",
      "parameters": [],
      "representative_content": "在空气中，金球、铅球、铜球等重材料球从100腕尺落下，金球领先铜球不超过四指。",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "obs.air",
          "module": "default",
          "package": "galileo_fine",
          "version": "4.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "observation",
      "knowledge_type": "claim",
